commentText: Add the "SameSite" attribute to the cookie._@see RFC6265 bis

Add the "SameSite" attribute to the cookie._

This limits the scope of the cookie such that it will only be_attached to same site requests if {@code "Strict"} or cross-site_requests if {@code "Lax"}._@see RFC6265 bis
